# The attempt to insert wood into the Wooden Chest has failed because I mistakenly referenced the position of the tree instead of the chest itself.
#
# To store the wood properly, I need to specify the Wooden Chest as the target for the insertion. 
# I will retrieve the position of the Wooden Chest and then attempt to insert the wood again.

# Getting the position of the Wooden Chest to insert wood into it.
wooden_chest_position = Position(x=0.5, y=0.5)  # Position where the Wooden Chest was placed.

# Attempting to insert 3 wood into the Wooden Chest.
insert_item(Prototype.Wood, target=wooden_chest_position, quantity=3)  # Insert 3 wood into the Wooden Chest.
